author: Natasha Patel
title: Priyanka Chopra Sat Front Row At NYFW In A Seriously Cool Outfit
text:
Embed from Getty Images 
Wearing a Prabal Gurung creation from the Spring 2017 collection; PC is spotted in a noir georgette t-shirt with gunmetal script embroidery with released chains that read, “ They Threw Things At Me Then, But They Were Not Roses ”. She paired its with a heather grey printed silk cady asymmetric handkerchief hem curved seam skirt with Nepali ring detail near the slit. 
FYI, the slit was HOT. And came with a side of thigh-high boots…
